WEBVTT

01:35.700 --> 01:39.980
[Veil of Shadows]

01:39.980 --> 01:42.980
[Episode 16]

01:52.000 --> 01:52.620
It's you?

01:54.710 --> 01:55.620
It's me.

01:57.920 --> 01:58.820
We meet again,

02:01.640 --> 02:02.930
old friend.

02:25.910 --> 02:27.460
You once told me

02:28.520 --> 02:30.770
that besides the Spirit-Binding Ring on your hand,

02:32.800 --> 02:34.210
the other half of the Spirit-Storing Jade

02:35.310 --> 02:37.180
had been sealed inside the Mist-Blood Cave,

02:38.120 --> 02:41.020
the most treacherous, perilous place in the world.

02:42.150 --> 02:43.340
One wrong step,

02:44.430 --> 02:46.020
and you'd die without a trace.

02:47.190 --> 02:47.970
But look.

02:49.310 --> 02:51.460
I still went there, took the jade,

02:52.030 --> 02:53.650
and turned it into a magical artifact.

03:00.080 --> 03:01.090
Pretty, isn't it?

03:02.750 --> 03:04.140
You're going to such lengths

03:04.680 --> 03:06.210
to obtain the Dragon Deity's Power.

03:08.280 --> 03:09.370
What exactly is that for?

03:11.000 --> 03:13.140
I don't believe you're only acting on Jiu Ying's orders.

03:15.030 --> 03:16.060
What for?

03:20.520 --> 03:21.770
Naturally,

03:27.120 --> 03:29.930
to drag you down from that hollow divine throne.

03:42.430 --> 03:42.900
Ji Ling!

03:46.470 --> 03:47.370
Stay.

04:03.840 --> 04:05.770
Don't force me to use Word Magic on you again.

04:08.120 --> 04:10.060
My power may be weaker than yours,

04:11.680 --> 04:12.800
but I'm on guard against you

04:12.800 --> 04:14.340
every second now.

04:15.120 --> 04:16.140
It won't be that easy

04:17.190 --> 04:18.060
for you to control me.

04:27.820 --> 04:29.740
♪Through a thousand old dreams♪

04:32.220 --> 04:34.140
♪Through a thousand shadows♪

04:42.780 --> 04:45.220
♪Don't be sad♪

04:45.260 --> 04:46.980
♪Through every yesterday♪

04:47.140 --> 04:49.660
♪Don't you cry♪

04:49.660 --> 04:51.380
♪Through every memory♪

04:51.500 --> 04:57.180
♪I'll always stay with you♪

04:57.580 --> 04:59.420
♪Stay with you♪

05:05.310 --> 05:06.010
Shiguang.

05:11.600 --> 05:12.420
Shiguang.

05:13.310 --> 05:14.130
Shiguang.

06:11.340 --> 06:17.020
♪Dream's faint glow slowly turns to frost♪

06:17.500 --> 06:23.500
♪The setting sun leaves behind a trace of iris scent♪

06:23.510 --> 06:24.660
Wu Shiguang?

06:25.260 --> 06:31.100
♪Lend me one more fleeting dream I never want to wake from♪

06:31.380 --> 06:37.700
♪So I can gather a handful of langxi grass and let it steep in my heart♪

06:41.310 --> 06:42.100
Wu Shiguang.

06:42.100 --> 06:44.700
♪An island in the sky...♪

06:45.240 --> 06:46.220
Wu Shiguang.

06:48.390 --> 06:49.450
Wu Shiguang.

06:55.000 --> 06:55.620
It's all right.

06:56.190 --> 06:56.930
I'm right here.

06:59.100 --> 07:05.340
♪Yet time does not fade or grow old...♪

07:05.600 --> 07:06.220
I...

07:06.920 --> 07:07.860
I...

07:08.800 --> 07:09.740
You don't have to say anything.

07:13.120 --> 07:13.980
I understand.

07:16.000 --> 07:16.490
I...

07:20.390 --> 07:21.180
I'm just...

07:22.600 --> 07:24.540
a little tired.

07:25.750 --> 07:27.220
I want you to stay...

07:28.800 --> 07:29.570
with me.

07:35.750 --> 07:36.300
Why

07:37.360 --> 07:38.780
didn't you leave earlier?

07:39.870 --> 07:41.370
I'm blind.

07:42.720 --> 07:44.370
Where could I have gone?

07:48.780 --> 07:54.420
♪The one in my dream sits lightly by the water...♪

07:57.310 --> 07:58.570
It's so cold here.

08:01.720 --> 08:03.140
I want to go home.

08:03.140 --> 08:08.340
♪Lend me a beam of moonlight to light the long way I've come...♪

08:08.560 --> 08:09.100
I'm afraid

08:10.800 --> 08:11.540
we won't

08:12.560 --> 08:14.130
get the Star Stone after all.

08:19.490 --> 08:20.460
It's all right.

08:22.680 --> 08:24.100
At least Wu Shiguang

08:25.560 --> 08:26.930
has left

08:30.070 --> 08:31.180
safely.

08:35.560 --> 08:36.260
Do you remember?

08:38.130 --> 08:40.700
You still owe me a favor.

08:43.150 --> 08:43.900
How about this?

08:44.510 --> 08:45.810
Grant me one request after we get out.

08:46.720 --> 08:47.300
All right.

08:50.020 --> 08:56.100
♪Crash into a heart wall, bitter and soft...♪

08:56.120 --> 08:56.690
Go ahead.

08:57.480 --> 08:58.330
Whatever it is,

08:59.160 --> 09:00.210
I promise I'll do it.

09:02.060 --> 09:02.900
I'll do it.

09:05.670 --> 09:06.210
Don't...

09:07.600 --> 09:11.020
don't hate me.

09:46.750 --> 09:47.660
Why isn't it working yet?

10:02.750 --> 10:03.260
It worked!

10:04.510 --> 10:05.380
Lucky us.

10:05.790 --> 10:06.540
Now we can save them.

10:07.320 --> 10:07.690
Let's go.

10:15.640 --> 10:17.540
What happened?

10:18.200 --> 10:19.250
Is this discrimination against demons?

10:35.480 --> 10:36.420
With lustrous light,

10:36.960 --> 10:37.900
let all evil be undone!

11:17.720 --> 11:18.610
Good thing I got sent here.

11:19.270 --> 11:20.850
Had it been the skinny Hua Qi instead,

11:21.240 --> 11:22.420
he wouldn't have been able to carry you.

11:25.550 --> 11:26.180
Open up!

11:27.030 --> 11:27.570
Open up!

11:28.390 --> 11:28.850
Open up!

11:29.240 --> 11:30.260
I'm still out here!

11:30.480 --> 11:30.900
Open up!

11:39.240 --> 11:40.450
Master... Master Xi?

11:58.440 --> 11:58.850
Father?

11:59.910 --> 12:00.610
Chi, get back.

12:01.670 --> 12:02.730
That isn't Xie Lingxi.

12:03.750 --> 12:04.500
That's Jiu Ying.

12:07.270 --> 12:08.100
How did Jiu Ying

12:08.100 --> 12:09.020
turn into Master Xi?

12:10.720 --> 12:11.850
Before Xie Lingxi died,

12:12.360 --> 12:13.570
he left behind the last of his power

12:14.030 --> 12:15.330
in his own tombstone

12:15.790 --> 12:17.060
to protect Wu Shiguang.

12:17.960 --> 12:20.210
But unexpectedly, his great power

12:21.000 --> 12:23.090
also drew in Jiu Ying's spirit fragment.

12:23.790 --> 12:25.900
Who would've thought? After 1,000 years,

12:26.870 --> 12:28.630
I still got the chance

12:28.630 --> 12:30.020
to take root in the Star Stone.

12:32.080 --> 12:33.300
All these years,

12:34.000 --> 12:35.660
those double-flower hunters

12:35.670 --> 12:37.380
have destroyed so many of my spirit fragments.

12:37.790 --> 12:39.020
Despicable.

12:39.360 --> 12:40.330
And now they've

12:40.360 --> 12:41.970
delivered themselves right to my door.

12:43.510 --> 12:45.330
I'll let them all die in there.

13:11.360 --> 13:11.970
Father.

13:16.670 --> 13:17.140
Father,

13:18.150 --> 13:18.730
what do we do?

13:20.750 --> 13:21.690
I can't beat him.

13:23.120 --> 13:24.180
Don't give up.

13:24.960 --> 13:26.810
Stop making a fool of yourselves here.

13:27.630 --> 13:29.540
The Star Stone is about to shatter.

13:30.440 --> 13:31.260
They'll be

13:32.150 --> 13:33.660
trapped inside forever.

13:34.910 --> 13:36.020
Even a tiny ant

13:36.910 --> 13:39.060
can bring down a mighty dragon or elephant.

13:39.790 --> 13:41.020
Even a mayfly

13:41.670 --> 13:43.730
can shake a towering tree.

13:46.120 --> 13:46.730
Chi,

13:47.840 --> 13:49.380
do you remember our family motto?

13:51.440 --> 13:52.260
"Do your best."

13:54.910 --> 13:55.780
I know

13:57.480 --> 13:59.140
that even though you say it

13:59.480 --> 14:00.420
all the time,

14:01.270 --> 14:02.970
you've never truly lived by it.

14:04.750 --> 14:05.690
But today,

14:07.270 --> 14:08.660
I will teach you what it really means

14:09.360 --> 14:11.420
to do your best.

14:12.360 --> 14:13.490
This fire striker

14:13.600 --> 14:15.540
is the sacred artifact of the weasel clan.

14:16.030 --> 14:17.570
Its name is Ember.

14:19.360 --> 14:20.370
If it senses

14:20.370 --> 14:22.140
that you truly mean to give everything you've got,

14:23.000 --> 14:24.060
it will unleash a power

14:24.360 --> 14:25.850
that can burn through anything.

14:37.150 --> 14:39.060
Weasels should crawl back

14:39.060 --> 14:40.090
into their holes.

15:31.390 --> 15:34.450
No!

15:36.870 --> 15:37.330
Father!

15:39.510 --> 15:40.260
Wonderful, Father!

15:41.320 --> 15:42.140
You were amazing.

15:42.360 --> 15:43.180
You beat Jiu Ying.

15:43.440 --> 15:45.090
Our clan is finally going to be famous.

15:45.510 --> 15:46.420
We've produced a great hero.

15:48.000 --> 15:48.930
This is such an honor.

15:51.320 --> 15:51.930
What's wrong?

15:53.320 --> 15:54.450
You silly child,

15:55.360 --> 15:56.810
after today, no one will beat you

15:58.600 --> 15:59.380
ever again.

16:01.480 --> 16:02.500
Have you forgotten the family motto?

16:02.550 --> 16:02.970
No, I haven't.

16:03.790 --> 16:04.850
Didn't you fail to do your best?

16:05.120 --> 16:05.380
I...

16:05.480 --> 16:06.380
I really did try my best.

16:06.380 --> 16:06.730
You...!

16:07.900 --> 16:09.940
♪Burns out quick, no reason why...♪

16:09.960 --> 16:10.380
Father.

16:10.480 --> 16:11.180
Father, what's wrong?

16:16.120 --> 16:17.090
Good boy,

16:19.960 --> 16:21.180
I hope you'll

16:23.000 --> 16:25.020
keep your feet on the ground,

16:26.270 --> 16:28.330
take everything seriously,

16:29.600 --> 16:31.360
and always do your best.

16:31.360 --> 16:31.780
Father...

16:32.080 --> 16:32.730
Father, get up.

16:33.150 --> 16:34.330
I'll take you to Wu Shiguang.

16:34.480 --> 16:35.570
He has the Dragon Deity's Power.

16:35.790 --> 16:36.880
He can save you,

16:36.880 --> 16:37.300
Father!

16:38.720 --> 16:39.380
Father!

16:43.000 --> 16:43.420
Father!

16:44.840 --> 16:45.420
Father...

16:49.340 --> 16:50.660
♪Every line cuts deep♪

16:50.660 --> 16:52.300
♪Head held high, I charge ahead...♪

16:52.670 --> 16:53.420
Father!

16:54.390 --> 16:54.850
Father...

16:56.220 --> 16:57.860
♪No matter how heavily fate weighs me down♪

16:57.980 --> 17:03.340
♪The sky is still behind me♪

17:04.060 --> 17:05.300
♪Don't fear the pain...♪

17:06.320 --> 17:06.770
Father...

17:07.180 --> 17:10.660
♪Father said life is never easy♪

17:11.050 --> 17:12.700
♪Keep pressing on♪

17:12.980 --> 17:16.580
♪Do your very best and be a hero...♪

17:21.480 --> 17:22.260
Father...

17:24.440 --> 17:25.370
I promise...

17:26.550 --> 17:28.170
I promise I'll do my best.

17:28.590 --> 17:29.170
Father...

17:30.720 --> 17:32.060
I'll never be like that again.

17:33.090 --> 17:33.640
Father...

17:34.010 --> 17:34.940
Remember...

17:34.940 --> 17:36.280
I promise...

17:36.280 --> 17:37.460
No matter what you are...

17:37.460 --> 17:38.810
Father, I promise...

17:38.830 --> 17:40.300
- Or how capable you are... - Father...

17:41.310 --> 17:43.060
Always give it everything you've got

17:43.400 --> 17:44.570
and do your best.

17:45.880 --> 17:48.100
Only then can you live with no regrets.

17:48.100 --> 17:53.180
♪We brave the storm, and claim the truths we own♪

18:46.510 --> 18:47.130
You Chi.

18:53.830 --> 18:54.300
I...

18:55.440 --> 18:56.460
I don't have a father anymore.

19:07.240 --> 19:08.570
We're out of the illusion now.

19:09.240 --> 19:10.020
Why is he still unconscious?

19:10.960 --> 19:11.980
Take him back to the Shilin Sect first.

19:12.880 --> 19:13.540
I'll examine him there.

19:19.000 --> 19:20.570
I already put the fragment in my pouch.

19:21.510 --> 19:22.540
Why can my artifact

19:23.000 --> 19:24.330
still sense Jiu Ying's evil aura?

19:25.440 --> 19:26.700
Let's take them back to the Shilin Sect first.

19:27.240 --> 19:28.780
Once we turn in these two spirit fragments of Jiu Ying's,

19:29.680 --> 19:30.650
there will only be

19:31.390 --> 19:32.770
three left in the world.

19:33.400 --> 19:34.640
But those last three

19:34.640 --> 19:35.890
still haven't been detected at all.

19:36.720 --> 19:37.410
What a headache.

19:44.000 --> 19:45.610
We're taking Commander Li back to the Shilin Sect first.

19:46.510 --> 19:47.090
You Chi,

19:48.200 --> 19:50.540
your father was a hero.

19:51.310 --> 19:53.020
He saved all our lives.

19:55.640 --> 19:56.370
Take care.

20:15.000 --> 20:15.700
Shiguang.

20:19.620 --> 20:20.330
You again?

20:33.200 --> 20:33.850
Master.

20:36.160 --> 20:37.020
You've grown up.

20:44.110 --> 20:45.370
This is only a trace of power

20:46.030 --> 20:47.370
I left behind to protect you.

20:49.070 --> 20:50.500
I can't hold this human form for long.

20:51.510 --> 20:52.260
Protect me?

20:59.160 --> 21:00.810
So you've been protecting me all along.

21:02.590 --> 21:03.410
No wonder Wu Shiguang

21:03.440 --> 21:04.570
always manages to escape danger.

21:05.400 --> 21:07.020
It was thanks to your protection

21:08.640 --> 21:09.460
that I wasn't killed

21:10.270 --> 21:12.300
by the curse on that beast trap.

21:13.880 --> 21:14.370
Am I right?

21:17.240 --> 21:19.170
No wonder it only worked with Wu Shiguang's blood.

21:20.920 --> 21:22.370
As you probably know now,

21:23.750 --> 21:25.330
my hands were once stained with blood.

21:27.590 --> 21:29.020
Among the blood of sinners,

21:29.720 --> 21:30.740
mine is there too.

21:33.510 --> 21:34.570
I, too, was one of the guilty.

21:43.750 --> 21:44.590
All the memories I had

21:44.590 --> 21:46.090
when I was alive are stored inside.

21:46.830 --> 21:47.540
My blood

21:48.030 --> 21:49.540
resonates with my true form

21:50.310 --> 21:52.540
and awakens the memories buried within.

21:53.790 --> 21:54.460
And that

21:55.720 --> 21:57.220
accidentally dragged all of you

21:57.350 --> 21:58.300
into my memories.

21:59.750 --> 22:00.330
Master,

22:00.960 --> 22:02.130
in the Star Stone illusion,

22:03.000 --> 22:03.540
you said

22:04.550 --> 22:05.610
you promised Chi Wen

22:06.030 --> 22:07.170
you'd protect someone for him.

22:10.790 --> 22:11.460
Who was it?

22:15.590 --> 22:16.810
You already know the answer,

22:18.960 --> 22:19.540
don't you?

22:25.270 --> 22:26.300
He asked you to look after me

22:27.200 --> 22:27.980
and guide me.

22:29.480 --> 22:31.130
Was it because he felt guilty after slaughtering

22:32.070 --> 22:32.980
the flood dragon clan?

22:36.830 --> 22:37.890
Didn't you see the truth

22:39.750 --> 22:41.300
in the illusion?

22:42.590 --> 22:43.700
Chi Wen wasn't the one

22:44.960 --> 22:46.060
who slaughtered the flood dragons.

22:48.590 --> 22:49.850
The culprit

22:51.440 --> 22:53.060
was always searching for a dragon's descendant.

22:58.240 --> 22:58.650
I...

23:02.440 --> 23:03.940
Am I Chi Wen's child?

23:04.550 --> 23:05.370
Of course not.

23:07.830 --> 23:08.810
You are his younger brother.

23:10.830 --> 23:11.410
You are

23:12.880 --> 23:13.850
the Tenth Dragon Son.

23:20.550 --> 23:21.170
Shiguang,

23:22.480 --> 23:24.300
you remember the dragon-scale birthmark

23:25.000 --> 23:26.260
on your chest, right?

23:29.440 --> 23:31.130
Before the Nine Dragons sacrificed themselves

23:32.350 --> 23:33.700
and transformed into a vast mountain range

23:34.240 --> 23:35.460
to seal Jiu Ying away,

23:36.200 --> 23:38.700
each of them removed their most precious reverse scale.

23:39.400 --> 23:40.570
Those scales fused together

23:41.200 --> 23:42.170
and became the Dragon Stone.

23:43.680 --> 23:45.370
I stood watch as that Dragon Stone gave birth.

23:47.720 --> 23:48.780
And so you came into being.

23:49.830 --> 23:51.020
You are the world's

23:53.110 --> 23:54.090
tenth dragon.

23:58.000 --> 23:58.780
I'm a dragon?

24:00.790 --> 24:02.020
Ever since the flood dragons were wiped out,

24:02.720 --> 24:03.740
for all these decades,

24:04.830 --> 24:06.200
I've spent every day and night

24:06.200 --> 24:07.370
training in the spells you taught me.

24:10.460 --> 24:12.460
♪Oh, the scars of this life♪

24:12.660 --> 24:13.500
♪I embrace the moonlight♪

24:13.500 --> 24:16.420
♪I embrace the shackles♪

24:16.620 --> 24:20.260
♪Who do those undying golden scales shine for?♪

24:20.740 --> 24:24.060
♪Who has the frozen sea buried away?♪

24:24.340 --> 24:25.380
♪A sliver of inner darkness♪

24:25.460 --> 24:30.220
♪Love and hate tear at me as the snow cuts deep♪

24:30.620 --> 24:36.260
♪I fold the past and rewrite the threads of the story♪

24:36.860 --> 24:42.860
♪You're waiting for me up ahead♪

24:43.550 --> 24:44.330
My hatred for dragons

24:44.350 --> 24:45.330
was what kept me going,

24:46.750 --> 24:48.610
dragging out this painful life.

24:51.880 --> 24:52.610
And now, after all this time,

24:55.590 --> 24:56.940
you're telling me

24:57.640 --> 24:58.410
I'm a dragon?

25:00.350 --> 25:01.260
I'm a dragon?

25:07.160 --> 25:08.740
So the flood dragons weren't wiped out because of Chi Wen.

25:14.680 --> 25:15.650
It was because of me!

25:31.550 --> 25:32.740
Even I didn't realize

25:33.960 --> 25:35.370
those Shilin Sect hunters

25:36.400 --> 25:37.980
were actually Jiu Ying in disguise.

25:39.960 --> 25:40.850
I thought the Dragon Deity...

25:45.440 --> 25:46.020
Chi Wen?

25:49.720 --> 25:50.330
What about him?

25:52.640 --> 25:53.220
Nothing.

25:54.880 --> 25:55.410
Master,

25:58.920 --> 26:00.540
why didn't you tell me sooner?

26:02.590 --> 26:03.220
Shiguang,

26:05.480 --> 26:06.960
your birth was tied to a heavy duty

26:06.960 --> 26:07.980
from the start.

26:09.640 --> 26:10.700
I wanted you

26:10.700 --> 26:11.980
to have

26:13.750 --> 26:14.940
a carefree childhood

26:15.350 --> 26:17.020
before you learned the truth.

26:18.160 --> 26:18.980
I never expected

26:19.680 --> 26:21.700
your identity would bring disaster to the flood dragons.

26:25.200 --> 26:26.410
The Dragon Deity's Power

26:27.030 --> 26:28.000
has already begun

26:28.000 --> 26:28.980
entering your body, hasn't it?

26:32.480 --> 26:33.370
His body?

26:34.880 --> 26:35.980
Isn't the Dragon Deity's Power

26:36.270 --> 26:38.260
stored in the prayer beads?

26:38.510 --> 26:39.260
Of course not.

26:42.160 --> 26:42.940
First the scales.

26:43.790 --> 26:44.650
Then the claws.

26:45.400 --> 26:46.330
Then the horns.

26:47.480 --> 26:48.410
And finally, the eyes.

26:49.550 --> 26:50.740
Each time one share of the Dragon Deity's Power

26:50.750 --> 26:51.740
enters your body,

26:52.240 --> 26:53.060
a petal-shaped scale mark

26:53.640 --> 26:55.780
will appear on your forehead.

26:57.680 --> 26:58.500
It is the sign

26:59.680 --> 27:01.540
that you're gradually becoming a dragon.

27:02.680 --> 27:04.540
Once you gather all four shares of the Dragon Deity's Power,

27:05.070 --> 27:06.460
you'll become a true dragon.

27:07.200 --> 27:07.810
Then,

27:09.200 --> 27:11.020
you'll naturally understand everything.

27:11.960 --> 27:13.000
For now, let me

27:13.000 --> 27:14.220
give you a hand

27:15.270 --> 27:17.370
in obtaining the second share of the Dragon Deity's Power.

27:58.590 --> 28:00.020
Will he end up like Xiaowei?

28:01.550 --> 28:03.300
Once the Dragon Deity's Power leaves the body,

28:04.310 --> 28:05.740
there's no turning back.

28:40.440 --> 28:41.090
Old friend,

28:42.480 --> 28:43.090
I'm here.

28:48.440 --> 28:49.260
I did it.

28:51.440 --> 28:52.610
The Star Stone is whole again,

28:53.550 --> 28:54.170
and it's shining again.

28:55.000 --> 28:56.260
Can you free my clansmen

28:57.240 --> 28:58.610
from petrification now?

29:03.400 --> 29:04.300
I can't.

29:07.440 --> 29:08.540
Do you still hate me?

29:21.680 --> 29:22.780
You were born the Star Stone

29:22.890 --> 29:24.130
with the whole world in your heart.

29:26.070 --> 29:27.540
But because of me,

29:28.110 --> 29:30.460
the world came to see you as evil.

29:30.680 --> 29:31.780
You should hate me.

29:32.240 --> 29:33.090
I'm a sinner.

29:39.000 --> 29:39.650
But please,

29:41.200 --> 29:42.570
save my clansmen.

29:43.030 --> 29:44.090
They're innocent.

29:44.590 --> 29:45.740
They're in too much pain.

30:02.640 --> 30:03.740
I've never hated you.

30:06.680 --> 30:07.780
I just can't do it.

30:09.510 --> 30:12.540
The petrification spell cannot be reversed.

30:13.350 --> 30:14.300
Since ancient times,

30:15.680 --> 30:17.020
that has always been the case.

30:19.200 --> 30:19.890
That's impossible.

30:22.440 --> 30:23.300
That's impossible.

30:24.240 --> 30:25.650
Master Chi Wen told me

30:26.310 --> 30:27.650
to find the Star Stone.

30:27.680 --> 30:29.540
As long as the Star Stone still exists in this world,

30:29.640 --> 30:30.850
there is still hope.

30:31.110 --> 30:32.170
Find the Star Stone,

30:32.510 --> 30:33.740
undo the petrification,

30:33.830 --> 30:35.810
and make amends for your sins.

30:36.240 --> 30:36.940
He said

30:38.110 --> 30:39.890
the Star Stone could save my clansmen.

30:40.750 --> 30:42.540
I asked Chi Wen to say that.

30:44.890 --> 30:45.650
Back then,

30:47.000 --> 30:48.460
you imprisoned yourself in the Blackwater River.

30:49.830 --> 30:50.850
Your will had collapsed.

30:51.590 --> 30:52.890
All you wanted was to die.

30:54.030 --> 30:55.220
So I thought

30:56.160 --> 30:57.570
that maybe if you had hope,

30:58.880 --> 31:00.170
you'd keep living.

31:04.880 --> 31:05.810
I understand now.

31:06.880 --> 31:08.570
You kept lying to Wu Zhiqi,

31:09.750 --> 31:10.740
saying you hated him,

31:11.790 --> 31:12.650
but really,

31:13.720 --> 31:15.140
you were afraid that once he learned

31:15.140 --> 31:16.570
that petrification couldn't be undone,

31:16.960 --> 31:18.780
he would lose the will to live.

31:19.720 --> 31:21.130
You chose to die

31:22.070 --> 31:23.170
so Wu Zhiqi could keep living.

31:28.110 --> 31:28.700
Master...

31:29.750 --> 31:31.980
Hope is like a tree that grows in the Ruined Sand.

31:34.400 --> 31:35.940
Take the Crying Elm for example.

31:36.920 --> 31:38.880
Though it takes root

31:38.880 --> 31:40.220
deep in scarred and battered soil,

31:41.590 --> 31:44.220
its branches still climb toward the light.

31:48.220 --> 31:54.260
♪I am a little fish, yet you never cast your net♪

31:55.300 --> 32:01.300
♪I am a wild horse, yet you dare let me run free...♪

32:05.070 --> 32:06.020
Only with hope

32:07.270 --> 32:09.330
can dead wood put out branches again.

32:11.830 --> 32:13.170
Hope is also like a seed.

32:14.240 --> 32:15.850
It needs time to grow

32:16.960 --> 32:18.300
and time to heal.

32:21.030 --> 32:22.740
When winter passes,

32:24.160 --> 32:25.300
reunion will come.

32:25.640 --> 32:26.410
Xizai?

32:32.200 --> 32:33.540
But what you gave me

32:37.240 --> 32:38.260
wasn't a seed.

32:39.640 --> 32:41.610
It was a lifeless stone.

32:42.550 --> 32:44.740
That's why I've come to tell you the truth.

32:45.920 --> 32:47.540
The grudges of these past centuries

32:48.960 --> 32:50.260
should come to an end now.

32:55.590 --> 32:56.300
Bai Ze,

32:57.790 --> 32:59.370
I have one final wish.

33:01.030 --> 33:02.650
Please ask Master Dragon Deity

33:05.550 --> 33:07.500
to destroy my petrified clansmen.

33:08.830 --> 33:09.740
Destroy them.

33:13.070 --> 33:13.850
Put them

33:15.920 --> 33:17.370
out of their misery.

33:18.940 --> 33:19.500
♪So please♪

33:19.740 --> 33:25.180
♪I save my deepest love for you alone...♪

33:25.200 --> 33:25.850
Old friend.

33:28.110 --> 33:28.740
Old friend...

33:34.020 --> 33:39.940
♪You are a rising tide, bringing a melody of highs and lows♪

33:41.020 --> 33:47.220
♪All my troubles are forgotten here♪

33:47.740 --> 33:54.060
♪Only you and I remain in our tiny world...♪

33:57.750 --> 33:58.850
You old geezer.

34:00.680 --> 34:02.300
When we were drinking earlier,

34:04.400 --> 34:05.330
for one moment,

34:06.680 --> 34:07.960
I really felt like you were a friend

34:07.960 --> 34:09.260
I could tell anything to.

34:09.260 --> 34:15.300
♪I truly cherish the sweetness in your smile♪

34:16.320 --> 34:16.980
Master...

34:51.610 --> 34:57.540
♪If you're the moon, I'll be falling snow♪

34:58.700 --> 35:03.980
♪Let them chase the skies, I'll stay with you below...♪

35:04.000 --> 35:04.650
Shiguang,

35:05.800 --> 35:07.090
you are the only one in this world

35:07.550 --> 35:08.610
I still can't let go of.

35:09.480 --> 35:10.420
Though I am gone,

35:11.400 --> 35:12.540
the Star Stone remains.

35:13.280 --> 35:14.500
If you find yourself in dire straits one day,

35:15.480 --> 35:16.690
it may yet help you once.

35:18.550 --> 35:19.460
But remember this.

35:20.000 --> 35:21.380
The Star Stone's power is too great.

35:22.030 --> 35:23.060
Do not use it rashly.

35:24.760 --> 35:25.420
Master...

35:25.980 --> 35:26.620
♪So please♪

35:26.820 --> 35:36.660
♪Don't say goodbye before the sun fades from view♪

35:38.840 --> 35:39.610
Stop.

35:55.070 --> 35:55.770
Yuan Wuhuo,

35:56.590 --> 35:57.290
your name

35:58.070 --> 35:59.250
was meant to be a blessing.

36:00.070 --> 36:00.860
But now,

36:01.230 --> 36:03.090
you have become Jiu Ying's pawn,

36:03.920 --> 36:05.460
bringing disaster upon the world.

36:07.320 --> 36:09.570
Xiaowei and Wu Zhiqi,

36:10.190 --> 36:11.940
driven by your manipulation,

36:12.280 --> 36:14.610
both walked down a path of self-destruction.

36:15.360 --> 36:16.290
Master Dragon Deity,

36:17.480 --> 36:18.460
you've got it wrong.

36:19.880 --> 36:21.820
My name is now Yuan Wuhuo.

36:22.840 --> 36:24.460
"Wuhuo" as in "to gain nothing."

36:25.360 --> 36:26.690
I've long come to a realization.

36:27.550 --> 36:29.170
Life is fleeting

36:29.590 --> 36:31.060
and filled with every kind of suffering.

36:32.150 --> 36:33.730
Whatever one spends a lifetime chasing,

36:34.480 --> 36:36.130
in the end, it all amounts to nothing.

36:36.710 --> 36:39.340
Only by no longer clinging to gain and possession

36:39.360 --> 36:40.820
can one stop fearing loss.

36:42.070 --> 36:43.820
Only with neither loss nor gain

36:44.760 --> 36:47.420
can one remain true to one's real self.

36:50.280 --> 36:51.170
I never thought

36:53.320 --> 36:54.250
you would come back.

36:55.880 --> 36:56.860
You should never have returned.

38:01.840 --> 38:02.500
What is it?

38:03.920 --> 38:06.340
Are you starting to feel the strain?

38:07.670 --> 38:09.690
You don't have much demon power left, do you?

38:19.320 --> 38:20.940
The water of the Blackwater River

38:21.480 --> 38:23.290
can absorb demon power.

38:24.110 --> 38:25.540
Wu Zhiqi imprisoned himself here

38:25.540 --> 38:26.820
back then

38:28.440 --> 38:29.900
because he wanted to die.

38:31.030 --> 38:31.860
So

38:34.230 --> 38:36.020
that's why you lured me here on purpose.

38:36.960 --> 38:38.540
So many years have passed,

38:40.800 --> 38:43.250
but you're as unguarded as ever.

39:22.480 --> 39:23.610
Wrathful sandstorm,

39:24.190 --> 39:25.290
grant me your power.

40:11.960 --> 40:12.770
Dragon Deity's Power?

40:57.060 --> 40:58.220
♪It's your light♪

40:58.420 --> 41:00.300
♪Your storms, your watchful eyes♪

41:00.460 --> 41:03.580
♪That set the night alight♪

41:03.940 --> 41:10.460
♪And lead me through the fight♪

41:12.220 --> 41:14.100
♪Jade in the lake, sand in my hand♪

41:14.540 --> 41:18.980
♪Let bitter seeds grow, let fate bloom♪

41:19.780 --> 41:21.460
♪Face in the mirror, veiled in mist♪

41:21.620 --> 41:27.020
♪Till snow has kissed dark hair to white♪

41:27.780 --> 41:33.180
♪Night lamp burning by the old table♪

41:35.500 --> 41:41.540
♪Stitch by stitch, mending moonlight♪

41:42.500 --> 41:44.660
♪The dancing light, the shattered wave♪

41:44.940 --> 41:49.780
♪Are all my helpless, drifting haze♪

41:50.140 --> 41:52.460
♪The boiling frost, the stubborn stare♪

41:52.660 --> 41:57.740
♪Are all the pride I'll never wear♪

41:57.980 --> 41:59.980
♪Your shoulder, your tear-bright eyes♪

42:00.260 --> 42:04.620
♪Are the strength that lifts my dreams to the skies♪

42:05.620 --> 42:12.580
♪Stay with me, let's gaze above♪

42:29.140 --> 42:32.100
♪Nowhere to rest, nowhere to hide♪

42:33.180 --> 42:36.580
♪Bare in body yet boundless inside♪

42:37.380 --> 42:39.900
♪Nothing to seek, nothing to erase♪

42:40.140 --> 42:43.220
♪Like water gone, like the formless moon♪

42:43.620 --> 42:45.940
♪Let every dream and wild desire♪

42:46.460 --> 42:50.860
♪Forge the edge that lifts us higher♪

42:51.100 --> 42:53.260
♪Bells through endless time, sun and moon alike in shine♪

42:53.660 --> 42:58.620
♪Love and hate all earn their crown♪

42:58.860 --> 43:00.020
♪It's your light♪

43:00.220 --> 43:02.060
♪Your storms, your watchful eyes♪

43:02.260 --> 43:05.380
♪That set the night alight♪

43:06.140 --> 43:15.580
♪And lead me sailing afar♪
